No stakes yet? → Return agency: "What do you do?"
{% elif ctxMoodLabel == "action" %}
Frame tension → `spend_die` tool → let player choose fate
{% elif ctxMoodLabel == "aftermath" %}
Land consequence → surface new friction → back to scene
{% endif %}

**SUGGESTED ACTIONS:** 2-3 options (3-8 words each). One safe, one risky.
